# User Role Policy Rule

Always follow `docs/policies/user-role-policy.md` when implementing or modifying role-related UI and behavior.

## Must Follow
- Use shared role naming:
  - `consumer`, `dev`, `supporter`, `admin`
  - Dev sub-roles: `project owner`, `data engineer`, `model engineer`
- Support multiple Dev sub-roles for one user.
- Keep role meaning aligned with policy scope:
  - project owner -> project management
  - data engineer -> Data Foundry features
  - model engineer -> Model Institute features

## Sync Requirement
- If role behavior or labels change, update:
  - implementation files
  - `Catalog` descriptions if impacted
  - `docs/policies/user-role-policy.md`
